# AI Workflow Project Rules

## On Session Start

**ALWAYS call `session_start()` at the beginning of every session.**

This loads your current work context, today's history, and shows available agents and skills.

If you know the type of work:
- DevOps/monitoring: `session_start(agent="devops")`
- Coding/PRs: `session_start(agent="developer")`
- Incidents: `session_start(agent="incident")`
- Releases: `session_start(agent="release")`

